""this is for java, c++,c# can reshape as necessary
"":ab ff <ESC>^d$ifor(int i=0;i<<ESC>pi.length;i++){<CR><CR>}//end for loop over array <ESC>pi[i]<ESC>==k==k==ji<TAB>
